377
00:28:37,591 --> 00:28:39,717
<font color="yellow">Baiklah, kami sudah datang.</font>

378
00:28:45,682 --> 00:28:48,893
<font color="yellow">Felipe!</font>

379
00:28:50,062 --> 00:28:54,315
<font color="yellow">Nenek, kembalilah dengan
