380
00:28:54,483 --> 00:28:55,650
<font color="yellow">Jauhkan wanita tua itu
dari baku tembak!</font>

381
00:28:55,818 --> 00:28:58,152
<font color="yellow">Nenek, dengarkan cucumu.</font>

382
00:28:58,320 --> 00:28:59,821
<font color="yellow">Ini bukan tempat yang tepat
untuk saat ini.</font>

383
00:28:59,988 --> 00:29:03,074
<font color="yellow">Tn. Gilbert sulit bernafas.</font>

384
00:29:03,242 --> 00:29:05,827
<font color="yellow">Dia perlu pereda asmanya.</font>

385
00:29:05,994 --> 00:29:07,453
<font color="yellow">Carlito tak menemukannya.</font>

386
00:29:07,621 --> 00:29:09,914
<font color="yellow">Dia perlu obatnya.</font>

387
00:29:13,127 --> 00:29:14,585
<font color="yellow">Felipe, tangani itu.</font>

388
00:29:14,753 --> 00:29:16,129
<font color="yellow">Dan ajak Nenek-mu bersamamu.</font>

389
00:29:18,298 --> 00:29:20,842
<font color="yellow">Siapa mereka?</font>

390
00:29:22,417 --> 00:29:23,594
<font color="yellow">Jangan bawa dia.</font>

391
00:29:23,762 --> 00:29:25,847
<font color="yellow">- Bu?
