498
00:36:32,107 --> 00:36:33,774
<font color="yellow">Persetan dengan kalian berdua.</font>

499
00:36:33,942 --> 00:36:36,277
<font color="yellow">Jangan ganggu aku sepanjang
malam ini.</font>

500
00:36:47,400 --> 00:36:49,039
<font color="yellow">Minta ikannya.</font>

501
00:36:49,207 --> 00:36:52,543
<font color="yellow">- Ini.
