502
00:36:55,130 --> 00:36:57,131
<font color="yellow">Aku rindu ini.</font>

503
00:37:07,350 --> 00:37:10,185
<font color="yellow">Aku harus bertanya.
Hal ini membuatku gila.</font>

504
00:37:10,353 --> 00:37:12,396
<font color="yellow">- Apa?
- Arloji itu.</font>

505
00:37:14,399 --> 00:37:16,025
<font color="yellow">Ada apa dengan arlojiku?</font>

506
00:37:16,192 --> 00:37:19,153
<font color="yellow">Aku melihatmu setiap hari,
di waktu yang sama...</font>

507
00:37:19,321 --> 00:37:21,697
<font color="yellow">...menyetel benda itu...</font>

508
00:37:21,865 --> 00:37:23,574
<font color="yellow">...seperti pendeta di pedesaan
yang berkhotbah.</font>

509
00:37:23,742 --> 00:37:25,826
<font color="yellow">Aku bertanya-tanya kepada
diriku sendiri.</font>

510
00:37:25,994 --> 00:37:28,787
<font color="yellow">- Aku tidak mengerti.
