520
00:37:59,402 --> 00:38:03,155
<font color="yellow">...yang telah diberikan secara
turun-temurun antar generasi.</font>

521
00:38:03,323 --> 00:38:05,616
<font color="yellow">Dia bilang...</font>

522
00:38:05,784 --> 00:38:09,787
<font color="yellow">"Aku berikan padamu rumah
peristirahatan terakhir...</font>

523
00:38:09,955 --> 00:38:12,539
<font color="yellow">...dari semua harapan dan hasrat...</font>

524
00:38:12,707 --> 00:38:16,085
<font color="yellow">...yang akan
mengisi kebutuhan pribadimu...</font>

525
00:38:16,252 --> 00:38:19,964
<font color="yellow">...sebaik dia mengisi kebutuhanku
